            <title>[LU-6353] Push Wireshark Support Upstream</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6353</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be good if we can push Wireshark support files upstream (Wireshark project) so we can delete them from our own repository.  The two files in question are packet_lnet.c and packet_lustre.c.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
